<p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to The Glenlivet Guardians!</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">Thank you for taking the time to attend the Legacy Tasting session of The Glenlivet whiskies at the Black Swan.  We hope that you have enjoyed the session.</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">We would like to take this opportunity to welcome you as a member of The Glenlivet Guardians, an exclusive league of aficionados with knowledge and passion for the single malt that started it all.</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">Created by enthusiasts for enthusiasts, a world of exclusive privileges with the Guardian programme awaits you, such as members-only access to private tastings, limited edition releases, invitations to unique events and exclusive downloads.</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">We look forward to seeing you at the next event for The Glenlivet Guardians.</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">For an experience of infinite elegance, indulge in the distinctive taste of our classic whisky range, The Glenlivet 12, 15, 18 and 25 Year Old.</p>
<p style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 11px;">Please <a style="color: #43ac8d;" href="mailto:theglenlivet.sg@pernod-ricard.com">contact us</a> for more information about exclusive promotions for The Glenlivet Guardians.</p>
